snippet.title: Sicko Sanctum 2 - 10 Golem
snippet.description:
Finished the all new Golem enemy! They are dangerous as they harvest turrets to use as their own powerful weapons. 

Likes and sharing really appreciated, subscribe to stay tuned to the future of Sicko Sanctum 2
